Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not there, no matter how hard you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a video tape that is proof of our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So of course I hid it some place very special in this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm keeping it as a guarantee that-you will divorce
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your wife and marry me instead. Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband will be coming home soc
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ou re 90mg < run mg WI 1 your college friends, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may relax on the sofa till then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, I don't understand adults, honestly
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's scary 'cuz even your relationship with your wife who you've been living
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,separately from all these years seem to look better...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that guy from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably working overtime because he can't fill his quota
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems her husband's finally come home
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ikm:home:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, hello dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, Morosumi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Soga, you're here already
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me use the bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you get the engine running while you're waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! If you're going out drinking, walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:17.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. And, would you like to come along too, for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No thank you, because I can't drink
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also want to watch the soccer game that will be aired at midnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SHl'd like to take a short nap too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The conversation that the two men would have over drinks drew some interest but
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long do you intend to stay fooling around out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and come on home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got a call from Ran, so we decided to head on home...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:47.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heiji! Just what do you think you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went out of my way 1 make dinner for you and it's all cold already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Morosumi residence where I accepted the work of the detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:13:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You just said you're headed home because you finished the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You just said you're headed home because you finished the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what we were planning to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but we passed a fire engine on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got concerned and headed back to the residence
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and found it blazing outrageously...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Morosumi residence...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this way, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,RRyoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like that woman didn't escape in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we just kept watching, this wouldn't have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two went outsto drink-right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not even-an-hour has past yet, and I wonder-why they came back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,True
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe they had a premonition of some kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, mommy, it came after all, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A red horse that causes fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey kid! How come you knew that a red horse was coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When and where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying! It was only the shadow of the horse, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:24.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was when I was watching\NKamen Yaiba in the living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Yaiba's first song started,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it suddenly got bright outside
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I looked outside and was surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A shadow of a horse about this big was on the curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which way I's your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the right of the burning house?\NOr, on the left?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:53.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:02.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A horse, by the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a red horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that the room ta boy was watching TV in, is this room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the shadow, of the horse showed up on this curtain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaimen Yaiba starts at 7:30 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it got bright during the opening of the program and the shadow was reflected
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The arsonist set fire and put-the horse in place a little after 7:30 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, at least we know that the arsonist was near this window about that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, so the horse set the fire after all, right, mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two hours later, the fire that took the life of\N"oko Moresumi W's finally extinguished
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you let me in just for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, will you at least tell me where the fire first broke out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal giving out a little info?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't do what I can't do, even if it's for you, Mr. Mouiril!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:13.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, the scene of a fire is not territory for the homicide division, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,0.0ld man fire of the 1st division?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mouri! How dare you call your former superior old man fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Former superior?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yuminaga of the Metropolitan
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police Arson Investigation\NDivision section 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you belonged to the homicide division?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:35.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used to be in the arson division for a little while...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure caused me a lot of agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time there's a fire you claim that it's arson and go out to the scene of the fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and step all over the personal effects left there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,God knows how many complaints\NI got of you from the fire department
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same goes for you too
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This fire is undoubtedly arson
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:17:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The red horse was found at the site of this fire too
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We checked it out with the forensic officers and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,found that it was a perfect match with the other three horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Yuminaga,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,isn't there a possibility that somebody who saw the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the incident in the newspaper or something tried copying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You foo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you make the exact same horse by just seeing it in the papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:23.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That plastic horse is made of the same mold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And is not sold anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so the arsonist probably took fun in making it himself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The arsonist was probably having fun challenging the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:35.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but somebody has been killed this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the fun's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, where did the fire start?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's this boy here, your assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, well, sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fire started in the hut beyond the right side of the house
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The storeroom with the window where the red horse was placed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were traces of kerosene poured on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the arsonist probably poured the kerosene
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in from the open window and set fire
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were a lot of strange footprints by
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the window of the room in the foreground of the storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we check the footprints carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll at least get to grab the tail of the arsonist
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:20.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your footprints are mixed up in the footprints there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm actually here because I was asked to come here by Mrs. Ryoko Morosumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:34.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the victim who died of the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She asked me to come check on a suspicious person
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who was doing something around her house late at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the lady said that it was just her imagination and told
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,us to leave, so we were watching her for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then a strange character who seemed to be a Feng Shui Sensei came by,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so having no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went into her yard and looked inside
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,through the window and saw a pretty bad scene
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty bad scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that this man was having an extra-marital affair with Ryoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and was ransacking the rooms looking
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for the video that was evidence of their affair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That act of yours sounds more than pretty bad to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, but I guess I'll have to take molds of your shoes later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you think that we're suspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fool! It's to discriminate your footprints with the arsonist's!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:32.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that man that had an affair with her, the only one that came by the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, four people came in all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man who had the affair and Ryoko's husband
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryoko's older sister who seems to be a fortune-teller.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A timid guy who came and left catalog of his store with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the Sensei of Feng Shui and\NRyoko's husband are not arsonists.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the testimony of the kid next door,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the red horse was placed by the window at exactly 7:30 pm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Sensei and her husband went out to drink at about 7:20 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the two couldn't have done it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we were contemplating for about 5 minutes whether to follow the two or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but at that time there was No smoke nor fire at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:19.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only concern is why those two came back so early despite having gone drinking
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that's because a neighbor called the husband's
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,cell phone and told him there! as a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which leaves the older sister who is a fortune-teller and the timid man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talking of fortunetelling,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the lady may be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What! Ryoko died?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a foolish child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:20:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I warned her time and again to be careful because
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw signs of disaster by fire in her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our father's funeral is not finished yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,still why is everybody crossing over like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you will excuse me asking, where were you at around 7:30 pm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, we are all under contract to start fortunetelling from 7:30 p.m
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one left is the timid man...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.82,0:21:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember any characteristics of that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.02,0:21:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His height was about 160 centimeters,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he was wearing round glasses\NHe seemed to be .in his forties.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Think he's an antique shop owner or something!
